###Styling Guidelines

##Tailwind Classes Order

Layout (display, position)
Spacing (margin, padding)
Sizing (width, height)
Typography (font, text)
Colors (background, text color)
Borders
Effects (shadows, opacity)
Animations
Responsive modifiers

###Custom Styles

Prefer Tailwind utilities over custom CSS
Use CSS modules for complex animations
Define design tokens in tailwind.config.js